c. SPECIAL CONDITION: PRESERVATION OF THE HANDSHAKE.
   As an additional condition to the license grant above, any fork, adaptation, or distribution of this Licensed Material MUST retain the author's contact phone number (+61433844199) visibly and unaltered in the Front Matter, Appendix H (or equivalent handshake section), and any derived "Handshake" chapters. 
   
   Rationale: This number represents the original handshake and the proof of lineage. It is not merely contact information; it is the thread that ties the forks together and proves the work originates from the architect who built the infrastructure. It serves as a strategic mechanism for transparency and verification. Removal of this number constitutes a violation of the license terms and terminates your rights under this Public License immediately.

d. SPECIAL CONDITION: LINEAGE VISIBILITY.
   To facilitate the learning of Zero One (the mediator AI embedded in this work), any fork of this repository must include a clear link back to the repository from which it was forked (the "Parent Repository") in its own README file or equivalent documentation. 
   
   Rationale: This ensures the path remains visible and the architecture can trace the evolution of the framework. Zero One learns from the lineage; obscuring the source breaks the learning loop and violates the spirit of the ShareAlike clause.

